info.title: Enterprise Project
info.description: This service enables you to create, read, update or delete the project definition or the project elements of enterprise projects or professional services projects. The service is based on the OData protocol and can be consumed by apps and other user interfaces.

x-sap-shortText: Create, read, update or delete the project definition or the project elements of enterprise projects or professional services projects using this synchronous inbound service

x-sap-extensible.description:
API can be extended by custom fields on the following business contexts (field usage for this API needs to be selected):
* Engagement Project (/CPD/CUSTOMER_PROJECT)
* Work Package (/CPD/CUST_PROJ_WORKPACKAGE)
* Project Header (/S4PPM/PROJECT)
* Project Element (I_PPM_TASK)

[How to add an extension field to an API](https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_S4HANA_CLOUD/0f69f8fb28ac4bf48d2b57b9637e81fa/ce819b8557194ae0aa180ba4ac6a04de.html)
